long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Unleash the power of the Gray Ravens with this dynamic Chrome extension that brings your favorite squad to your new tab!

The Gray Ravens live wallpaper extension immerses you in the futuristic world of Punishing: Gray Raven, capturing the intense energy of this elite team. With a sleek design that lets the stunning live wallpaper shine, this extension enhances your browsing experience while providing essential tools to keep you efficient and organized.

Navigate easily with a Google search bar, customized shortcuts to your favorite sites, and a clock-date display to keep track of time.

Key Features:
Live Wallpaper showcasing the Gray Ravens team
Google Search Bar for quick browsing
Customizable site shortcuts for efficient access
Clock-Date display for time updates

Dive into the world of Gray Ravens with every new tab! For more wallpapers, explore Gameograf.com to find your favorite themes.
